================================================================================
Third-party model weights
================================================================================

Gods Eye downloads neural-network weights at first run; they are NOT bundled in
this repository and carry their own licenses. Each must be reviewed before
redistribution.

- Depth Anything V2 — Metric, Small (ViT-S)
  Upstream: https://github.com/DepthAnything/Depth-Anything-V2
  Code + Small-tier weights: Apache-2.0.
  CAVEAT (do not assert away): upstream issue #320 flags unresolved training-
  data provenance (e.g. Hypersim / Virtual KITTI dataset terms) for commercial
  use. Gods Eye treats these weights as "permissive label, unverified data
  provenance." A clean-provenance replacement is a tracked goal; the runtime
  exposes `--model-path` so a cleared-weights checkpoint can be swapped in.
  NOTE: only the *Small* tier is Apache-2.0. The Base/Large/Giant tiers and the
  larger metric checkpoints are CC-BY-NC-4.0 and are NOT shipped or supported.

Reference-only models (NOT shipped — non-commercial / research licenses; used,
if at all, solely as offline evaluation ground truth):
  - Apple Depth Pro (apple-amlr, research-only)
  - UniDepth V2 (CC-BY-NC-4.0)
  - Metric3D V2 (BSD, non-commercial)
